    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047750/extras/925f50bf4f74d9e7dd2e2a8542c971da.poster.avif?t=1769095048\" width=616 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047750/extras/925f50bf4f74d9e7dd2e2a8542c971da.webm?t=1769095048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047750/extras/925f50bf4f74d9e7dd2e2a8542c971da.mp4?t=1769095048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >广受好评的氛围游戏《FAR: Lone Sails》系列制作者 Okomotive 工作室携手《Firewatch》发行商 Panic 强强联合，为您呈上来自《Herdling》的全新冒险盛宴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与一众憨态可掬的萌兽结伴同行，共赴这场广袤远大的山岳征途。山径之中总有光怪陆离的危险悄然以待，各种意料之外的阻碍也将纷至沓来，勇敢前行，绝美的顶峰自会为你揭晓一切的神秘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047750/extras/2d7790835ab333b6b32985ab3ad7c42a.poster.avif?t=1769095048\" width=616 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047750/extras/2d7790835ab333b6b32985ab3ad7c42a.webm?t=1769095048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047750/extras/2d7790835ab333b6b32985ab3ad7c42a.mp4?t=1769095048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>本作特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引领并保护一群各色各异的嘉利牛翻山越岭，与这群可爱的犄角灵兽结下深厚感情</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游历壮美山川，漫步雾霭林海，探寻遗落山谷，登览雪域高原</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >磨练自身放牧本领，应对广泛威胁挑战，轻松解开环境谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与在你引领下振奋奔腾的牧群一同感受心潮澎湃的山野之息</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需辞藻，用这场跨越末世的漫长旅途谱写关乎信任、陪伴、乃至生存的动人篇章</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047750/extras/830b8066669b03c1ca8844e96c830bb8.poster.avif?t=1769095048\" width=616 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047750/extras/830b8066669b03c1ca8844e96c830bb8.webm?t=1769095048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047750/extras/830b8066669b03c1ca8844e96c830bb8.mp4?t=1769095048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
